006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.atomic;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.function.InvalidValueForCastFunctionException;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012public interface IStringItem extends IAnyAtomicItem {
013  /**
014   * Construct a new item using the provided string {@code value}.
015   *
016   * @param value
017   *          a string value
018   * @return the new item
019   */
020  @NonNull
021  static IStringItem valueOf(@NonNull String value) {
022    return new StringItemImpl(value);
023  }
024
025  /**
026   * Cast the provided type to this item type.
027   *
028   * @param item
029   *          the item to cast
030   * @return the original item if it is already this type, otherwise a new item
031   *         cast to this type
032   * @throws InvalidValueForCastFunctionException
033   *           if the provided {@code item} cannot be cast to this type
034   */
035  @NonNull
036  static IStringItem cast(@NonNull IAnyAtomicItem item) {
037    return item.asStringItem();
038  }
039
040  @Override
041  default IStringItem asStringItem() {
042    return this;
043  }
044
045  @Override
046  default IStringItem castAsType(IAnyAtomicItem item) {
047    return cast(item);
048  }
049
050  /**
051   * Compares this value with the argument. Ordering is in lexical dictionary
052   * order.
053   *
054   * @param other
055   *          the item to compare with this value
056   * @return a negative integer, zero, or a positive integer if this value is less
057   *         than, equal to, or greater than the {@code item}.
058   */
059  default int compareTo(@NonNull IStringItem other) {
060    return asString().compareTo(other.asString());
061  }
062
063  @Override
064  default int compareTo(IAnyAtomicItem other) {
065    return compareTo(other.asStringItem());
066  }
067}
